name: The Wardens
description:
Hidden behind their sinister armors and their white mantles, the Wardens patrol the vastness of the Tapestry, carrying out an eternal watch over the realm of realms.
No one knows what guides them or what is their true purpose, but most dreamers make sure to stay clear of them.
As for those who took these figures for allies and protectors, they are no longer around to bear witness to their foolishness.
